                  stroke-width="2"
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  stroke-linejoin="round"
                  aria-hidden="true"
                  ><rect x="3" y="3" width="18" height="18" rx="2"></rect><line
                    x1="12"
                    y1="3"
                    x2="12"
                    y2="21"></line><line x1="3" y1="12" x2="21" y2="12"></line></svg
                ></span
              >
              <div>
                <strong>Condensation Issues</strong>
                <p>
                  Condensation on windows or vents can signal humidity and ventilation imbalance
